# SauceDemo Test Automation (WebdriverIO)

This project contains automated UI tests for the Dynamic Content flow on https://www.saucedemo.com/ using WebdriverIO.

---

## 📌 Task Overview

### ✅ UC-1: Product Details Verification

- Login using:
  - username: `standard_user`
  - password: `secret_sauce`
- Select a product dynamically (e.g. "Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket")
- Navigate to Product Details page
- Validate:
  - Product Price matches Inventory page
  - Product Description matches Inventory page
- Add product to cart from Details page

---

### ✅ UC-2: Footer & Social Links

- Scroll to footer
- Verify presence of:
  - Twitter link
  - Facebook link
  - LinkedIn link
- (Bonus)
  - Verify each link opens correct URL in a new tab

---

