## 📥 Installation

```bash
git clone <your-repo-url>
cd <project-folder>
npm install
```

---

## ▶️ Running Tests

### Run all tests (Chrome + Firefox in parallel + additional Safari)

```bash
npx wdio run ./src/config/wdio.conf.js
```

---

### Run a specific test

```bash
npx wdio run ./src/config/wdio.conf.js --spec ./src/tests/specs/inventory.e2e.js
```

---

### Run in headed mode

```bash
npx wdio run ./src/config/wdio.conf.js --headed
```

---

## 📊 Test Report (Allure)

### 1. Run tests

```bash
npx wdio run ./src/config/wdio.conf.js
```

### 2. Generate report

```bash
npx allure generate allure-results --clean
```

### 3. Open report

```bash
npx allure open
```

