## 🎯 Key Implementation Details

### ✔ Page Object Model (POM)
Each page is separated into reusable classes.

---

### ✔ Dynamic Product Handling

```js
await inventoryPage.clickProduct('Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket');
```

---

### ✔ Locators Strategy

- CSS selectors → preferred
- XPath → dynamic elements

---

### ✔ Logging

```js
console.log(`Verifying product: ${productName}`);
```

---

### ✔ Parallel Execution

- Chrome
- Firefox
- Safari (Additional)

Configured in wdio.conf.js.

